quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  27,64,"Koo! Ni wina owuchachinjia ebiloonje, mana khandi abikalusia? Ne wina ulia ubakabilanga okhurula mwikulu nende khushialo? Koo! Aliho nyasaye wundi halala nende Nyasaye? Boola mbu: “Rere ebifune bienyu nikali mbu toto muboolanga obulaamba.”"
  27,65,"Boola mbu: “Abulaho uli mwikulu nende khushialo umanyile akefisile halali Nyasaye butswa.” Nabo kata shibamanyile mbu ni liina lwabakhalamusibwe tawe."
  27,66,"Nohomba balondelela obumanyi bwa mwikulu nibaba nende obwatoto bwa (amakhuwa) akomwikulu? Halali bo bali mubukanakani bwabu, halali bo ni abawofu khuka eyo."
  27,67,"Ne balia bakhaya baboola mbu: “Olwa khuliba liloba, nende bapapa befu, mbu khulilamusibwa?"
  27,68,"Toto khwalakwa kano efwe nende bapapa befu bakhale. Kano shini shiosishiosi tawe halali tsingano tsiakhale.”"
  27,69,"Boola mbu: “Chende khushialo mana mulole shinga indukho ya abandu ababii yali.”"
  27,70,"Ne olababeelelela tawe, ne olaba mubutinyu khulwa ebifwanga biabu biabakholanga tawe."
  27,71,"Ne baboolanga mbu: “Ne indache ino iliula liina toto nimuli mbu muboolanga obulaamba?”"
  27,72,"Boola mbu: “Kanyala okhubanyola ahambi hano akandi muukalia akamuyungubalilanga.”"
  27,73,"Ne toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi ni wetsimbabaasi khubandu, halali abaanji mubo shibakhupanga orio tawe."
  27,74,"Ne toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi amanyile muno akebilifu biabu bifisanga nende akabaretsanga habulafu."
  27,75,"Ne libulaho liefisa mwikulu nende khushialo halali lili mushitabu eshiokhwinoosia."
  27,76,"Toto Ikurani ino ikanilanga Abaana ba Israili amaanji akabawukhanangamwo."